    <!-- Privacy Policy Content -->
    <section class="privacy-content">
        <div class="container privacy-container">
            <div class="privacy-section">
                <h2>
                    <i class="fas fa-clipboard-list"></i>
                    What Data We Collect
                </h2>
                <p>When you use our services, we may collect:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li><strong>Personal Information:</strong> Your name, email address, and any other info you provide when signing up or contacting us.</li>
                    <li><strong>Usage Data:</strong> How you interact with our website or app (like pages visited, time spent).</li>
                    <li><strong>Communication Data:</strong> Any feedback or messages you send us.</li>
                    <li><strong>Technical Data:</strong> IP address, browser type and version, time zone setting, and other technology on the devices you use to access our services.</li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="privacy-section">
                <h2>
                    <i class="fas fa-cogs"></i>
                    How We Use Your Data
                </h2>
                <p>We use your information to:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Provide and improve our services specifically for you.</li>
                    <li>Communicate important updates, offers, or support messages (only if you agree to receive them).</li>
                    <li>Understand how you use our services to make them better and more intuitive.</li>
                    <li>Comply with legal obligations when necessary.</li>
                    <li>Prevent fraud and enhance the security of our services.</li>
                </ul>
                <p>We process your data only when we have a legal basis to do so, such as your consent, the necessity to perform a contract, or to comply with legal requirements.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="highlight-box">
                <h3>We NEVER Sell Your Data 🚫💸</h3>
                <p>Your privacy is sacred. We do NOT sell, trade, or rent your personal data to any business partners or third parties. Your info stays with us, safe and sound. Period. 🔒</p>
            </div>

            <div class="privacy-section">
                <h2>
                    <i class="fas fa-shield-alt"></i>
                    How We Protect Your Info
                </h2>
                <p>We care about your security! We implement a range of measures to protect your personal information:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Use modern security technologies and protocols to protect your info from unauthorized access.</li>
                    <li>Restrict access to your data only to our trusted team members who need it to help you.</li>
                    <li>Regularly review our systems to keep your data safe.</li>
                    <li>Implement encryption for data both in transit and at rest.</li>
                    <li>Conduct regular security audits and vulnerability assessments.</li>
                </ul>
                <p>While we strive to protect your personal data, we cannot guarantee absolute security of any information transmitted to us.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="privacy-section">
                <h2>
                    <i class="fas fa-sliders-h"></i>
                    Your Rights & Control
                </h2>
                <p>You're in charge! You can exercise the following rights regarding your personal data:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li><strong>Access:</strong> Request access to your personal data anytime.</li>
                    <li><strong>Correction:</strong> Update or correct your information if something's changed.</li>
                    <li><strong>Deletion:</strong> Ask us to delete your data if you want to leave us.</li>
                    <li><strong>Opt-out:</strong> Opt out of marketing emails or communications at any time.</li>
                    <li><strong>Restriction:</strong> Request restriction of processing your personal data.</li>
                    <li><strong>Portability:</strong> Request transfer of your data to another organization.</li>
                </ul>
                <p>To exercise any of these rights, please contact us using the information below.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="privacy-section">
                <h2>
                    <i class="fas fa-cookie-bite"></i>
                    Cookies & Tracking
                </h2>
                <p>We use cookies and similar tracking technologies to make your experience smoother and to understand how you use our services. Cookies help us:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Remember your preferences and login information</li>
                    <li>Analyze traffic and usage patterns</li>
                    <li>Improve website performance</li>
                    <li>Deliver personalized content</li>
                </ul>
                <p>You can control cookie settings through your browser. Please note that disabling cookies may affect the functionality of our services.</p>
                <p>We also use analytics services like Google Analytics to collect information about how visitors use our site.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="privacy-section">
                <h2>
                    <i class="fas fa-hourglass-half"></i>
                    How Long We Keep Your Data
                </h2>
                <p>We only keep your info as long as needed to provide our services or to comply with legal requirements. Our retention periods are based on:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>The purpose for which we collected the data</li>
                    <li>Legal obligations requiring data retention</li>
                    <li>The nature and sensitivity of the data</li>
                    <li>Potential risk of harm from unauthorized use or disclosure</li>
                </ul>
